+ Declaring Shapes
-   define a variable x with shape cloud
    x {shape: cloud} 
-   define a variable container shape page with another parallelogram y inside, separate blocks with ; or indentation  
    container { 
        shape: page 
        y { shape:parallelogram } 
    } or
    container: {shape : page; y: {shape : parallelogram}}

+ Connections 
-   first -- second: No arrow just line connection 
-   first -> second: Arrow from first to second shape: 
-   first <- second:  Arrow from second to first shape: 
-   first <-> second: Two way arrow 

